This file contains the set of changes that have gone into this program.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------
Minimac4 Changes:
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
--------------------------------------------------------------------------

Version : 1.0.2
Author  : Sayantan Das
Date    : March 3, 2017

        Updated the implementation of chromosome X so as to allow both 
	males and females to imputed together on non-PAR. Also implemented
	meta-imputation empirical dosage part.
	
--------------------------------------------------------------------------

Version : 1.0.1
Author  : Sayantan Das
Date    : Dec 5, 2016

        First version of minimac4. Lots of new features including 
	automated chunking, improved multi-threading, faster algorithm,
	efficient file I/O

--------------------------------------------------------------------------

